  "summary": "Exactly what it says on the tin.",
  "descriptionHtml": "Improving weapons and armor is totally unbalanced so I removed it.  If you want better gear, use better materials.  I suppose you could just not improve your stuff, but many people have insufficient self control.  Workbenches and grindstones are just furniture.  You can activate them to play the animation, but no menu will appear.  Also removes the blacksmithing tutorial quest.\r<br />\r<br />Optional files also makes it impossible to smith or enchant or just improve or enchant.  Use only one of the three.\r<br />\r<br />Obviously, this whole thing is kind of a non-solution that I just threw together.  I really don&#39;t know anymore why you would waste memory on this.  It might crash your game too, since it&#39;s not very well made.  Eventually I may make a system that actually fixes the crafting.  I know how I want to do it, but I don&#39;t like doing actual work, so look for it probably around never.",
